   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Appeal for Flood Victims of Bihar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Terrible Floods have hit Bihar again. Over 350 people have died.  Tens of thousand are homeless and do not have even a plastic sheet for shelter We need your help to provide Emergency Relief to reach out to 10,000 people.  We need to provide blankets , mosquito nets, food, clothes and medicines especially for children. With our trusted position with local government we can ensure aid reaches those most in need of it quickly and safely.</narrative>
  </description>
